Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US interference in UK politics
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xqtc
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Oct 1986
Labour policy on nuclear weapons could change US-UK alliance, says Weinberger. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.